#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Documents App</b>: Centralize supplier certificates, quality control "
"reports, and shipping manifests for easy\n"
"          retrieval during audits."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aplikasi Dokumen</b>: Pusatkan sertifikat supplier, laporan QC, dan "
"manifes pengiriman agar mudah\n"
"          diakses selama audit."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Fleet App</b>: Manage your delivery trucks and vans, tracking fuel logs, "
"maintenance schedules, and driver\n"
"          assignments in one place."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aplikasi Armada</b>: Kelola truk dan van pengiriman, pelacakan catatan "
"bahan bakar, jadwal perawatan, dan penugasan sopir\n"
"          hanya dari satu tempat."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Inventory App</b>: Master your stock with advanced features like Lots "
"&amp; Serial Numbers for traceability\n"
"          and Expiration Dates to enforce FEFO (First Expired, First Out) "
"removal strategies."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aplikasi Inventaris</b>: Kelola stok dengan fitur-fitur canggih seperti "
"Lot &amp; Nomor Seri untuk penelusuran\n"
"          dan Tanggal Kedaluwarsa untuk menerapkan strategi penghapusan FEFO "
"(First Expired, First Out)."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Invoicing App</b>: Streamline your billing with automated invoicing based "
"on delivered quantities, ensuring\n"
"          accurate financial records."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aplikasi Faktur</b>: Sederhanakan penagihan dengan faktur otomatis "
"berdasarkan jumlah yang dikirim untuk memastikan\n"
"          catatan keuangan selalu akurat."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Purchase App</b>: Automate your procurement process with reordering rules "
"that account for vendor lead times\n"
"          and seasonal demand spikes."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aplikasi Purchase</b>: Otomatiskan proses pengadaan dengan aturan "
"pemesanan ulang yang memperhitungkan waktu tunggu vendor\n"
"          dan lonjakan permintaan musiman."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Sales App</b>: Manage complex pricing structures with Pricelists, "
"allowing you to offer specific deals to\n"
"          restaurants, retailers, or wholesalers."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aplikasi Sales</b>: Kelola struktur harga yang kompleks dengan Daftar "
"Harga sehingga Anda dapat menawarkan penawaran khusus kepada\n"
"          restoran, pengecer, atau grosir."

