msgstr "Aktif"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add some Salt and Sugar to secure suppliers for longer on those sides."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan Garam dan Gula untuk mengamankan supplier lebih lama untuk sisi-"
"sisi tersebut."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:x_nutritional_facts,x_name:food_distribution.x_nutritional_facts_4
msgid "Added Sugar"
msgstr "Gula Tambahan"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All Manufacturing Orders here are Ready to manufacture by default but you "
"can play with\n"
"        the filters at top right of the screen to see them all."
msgstr ""
"Semua Pesanan Manufaktur di sini Siap untuk dimanufaktur secara default tapi "
"Anda dapat bermain dengan\n"
"        filter di pojok kanan atas layar untuk melihat semuanya."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Also order the Mayonnaise so you can fill those buckets with sauce."
msgstr ""
"Juga pesan Mayonnaise supaya Anda dapat mengisi ember tersebut dengan saus."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.x_nutritional_facts_search_view
msgid "Archived"
msgstr "Diarsipkan"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As a result, a single MO includes all manufacturing needs for the coming "
"days, ensuring customers will be delivered fresh products while you batch "
"their production!"
msgstr ""
"Oleh karena itu, satu MO mencakup semua kebutuhan manufaktur untuk beberapa "
"hari ke depan untuk memastikan pelanggan akan menerima produk segar "
"sementara Anda mengelompokkan produksinya!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As an Inventory Manager you need to make sure that the production team never "
"runs out of\n"
"          supply!"
msgstr ""
"Sebagai Manajer Inventaris Anda harus memastikan tim produksi tidak pernah "
"kehabisan\n"
"          suplai!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Assuming you received some ingredients and weeks after the supplier notifies "
"you of a quality alert about the lot PLE-001 of pasteurized liquid eggs."
msgstr ""
"Seandainya Anda menerima beberapa bahan baku dan beberapa minggu kemudian "
"supplier memberi tahu tentang peringatan kualitas terkait lot PLE-001 telur "
"cair pasteurisasi."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.food_distribution_inherit_report_lot_label
msgid "B.b."
msgstr "Baik sebelum"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Between production and deliveries, by default, the product picking is "
"organized in FIFO."
msgstr ""
"Antara produksi dan pengiriman, secara default, picking produk diatur di "
"FIFO."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:uom.uom,name:food_distribution.uom_uom_39
msgid "Box 8x 250g Tub"
msgstr "Box 8x 250g Tub"

#. module: food_distribution
