msgid "Bucket 5L"
msgstr "Ember 5L"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products, sale\n"
"      orders and more."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengunggah data demo modul ini, database Anda telah diisi dengan "
"beberapa produk,\n"
"      pesanan penjualan dan lebih banyak lagi."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.res_config_settings_form_view_inherited
msgid ""
"Capture food and drink data on product and leverage them in printed labels."
msgstr ""
"Rekam data makanan dan minuman pada produk dan manfaatkan data tersebut "
"untuk dicantumkan pada label cetak."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:x_nutritional_facts,x_name:food_distribution.x_nutritional_facts_3
msgid "Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Karbohidrat"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click on one of the Ready orders to produce some Mayonnaise."
msgstr "Klik pada satu pesanan Siap untuk membuat beberapa Mayonnaise."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Close Production button at the end of the tile when done with all "
"steps. Great\n"
"        you manufactured you first Mayonnaise batch!"
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol Tutup Produksi di kotak terakhir setelah menyelesaikan semua "
"langkah. Mantap,\n"
"        Anda telah memproduksi batch Mayonnaise pertama!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Confirm the Purchase Order when in agreement with your supplier."
msgstr ""
"Konfirmasi Purchase Order setelah mencapai kesepakatan dengan supplier Anda."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Confirm the order to close your deal."
msgstr "Konfirmasi pesanan untuk menyelesaikan transaksi."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.category,name:food_distribution.product_category_6
msgid "Containers"
msgstr "Kontainer"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create an Invoice, send it to your customer and confirm it to get paid for "
"your hard work!"
msgstr ""
"Buat Faktur, kirimkan ke pelanggan, dan konfirmasi untuk menerima pembayaran "
"atas kerja keras Anda!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Define dates to plan those smaller orders along the corresponding period to "
"smoothen the\n"
"        load and then proceed to the split.<br/>As a result, the initial "
"order has been split into\n"
"        multiple smaller orders."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan tanggal untuk merencanakan pesanan-pesanan kecil sepanjang periode "
"tersebut meratakan\n"
"        beban, lalu lanjutkan ke pembagian.<br/>Dengan begitu, pesanan awal "
"telah dibagi menjadi\n"
"        beberapa pesanan kecil."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.food_distribution_inherit_report_lot_label
