msgstr "Lot/Nomor Seri Demo"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.food_distribution_inherit_report_lot_label
msgid "Demo Product"
msgstr "Produk Demo"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Depending on your current stock level, an appropriate replenishment "
"suggestion will be\n"
"        created for the final product and its components via the indirect "
"demand, for instance here:\n"
"        the Bucket and the Dispenser, as well as the Mayonnaise down below."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung level stok Anda saat ini, saran pemulihan stok yang sesuai akan\n"
"        dibuat untuk produk akhir dan komponennya melalui permintaan tidak "
"langsung, misalnya di sini:\n"
"        Bucket dan Dispenser, serta Mayones di bawah ini."

