#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"First, you might want to fill in your estimated Forecasted Demand for your "
"finished\n"
"        products, in this case, Mayonnaise Bucket and Dispenser."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, isi estimasi Demand yang Diperkirakan untuk produk jadi Anda,\n"
"        yang dalam hal ini adalah Bucket dan Dispenser Mayones."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Follow as well the steps and close the production. Great, you now have some "
"products to\n"
"        ship to delight customers."
msgstr ""
"Ikuti juga langkah-langkahnya dan selesaikan produksi. Nah, sekarang Anda "
"memiliki beberapa produk untuk\n"
"        dikirim demi memenuhi kebutuhan pelanggan."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Follow the step from each operation to prepare your Mayonnaise batch."
msgstr ""
"Ikuti langkah-langkah dari setiap kegiatan operasional untuk menyiapkan "
"batch Mayones Anda."

