#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Some plan, others produce... Open the <strong>Shop Floor App</strong> to "
"manufacture\n"
"      products."
msgstr ""
"Ada yang di perencanaan, ada yang di produksi... Buka <strong>Aplikasi Shop "
"Floor</strong> untuk manufaktur\n"
"      produk."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Some rules are defined to easily resupply ingredients and containers."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa aturan ditetapkan untuk memudahkan pengisian ulang bahan dan wadah."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_7
msgid "Sugar"
msgstr "Sugar"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_2
msgid "Sunflower Oil"
msgstr "Minyak Bunga Matahari"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take advantage of the power of <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Manufacturing App</font>\n"
"        </strong> with Manufacture To\n"
"        Order (MTO) capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Manfaatkan keunggulan <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Aplikasi Manufaktur</font>\n"
"        </strong> dengan fitur Manufacture To\n"
"        Order (MTO)."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Bill of Material is accessible from the Manufacturing App Products menu."
msgstr ""
"Bill of Material (BoM) dapat diakses dari menu Produk di Aplikasi Manufaktur."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Dates section allows you to detail the expiration dates of your products."
msgstr ""
"Bagian Tanggal memungkinkan Anda untuk mencantumkan tanggal kedaluwarsa "
"produk."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Mixing tank work center is configured with setup and cleanup time. Take "
"advantage of\n"
"          this capability to optimize your operations!"
msgstr ""
"Pusat kerja tangki Mixing telah dikonfigurasi dengan waktu penyiapan dan "
"pembersihan. Manfaatkan\n"
"          kemampuan ini untuk mengoptimalkan operasional Anda!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The last 3 MO capture recent confirmed orders for potato salads with a start "
"date allowing to manufacture just in time."
msgstr ""
"3 MO terakhir mencatat pesanan salad kentang yang baru-baru ini dikonfirmasi "
"dengan tanggal mulai yang memungkinkan produksi tepat waktu."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The nutritional fact list is available from the Inventory App, Configuration "
"menu."
msgstr "Informasi nilai gizi tersedia di Aplikasi Inventaris, menu Konfigurasi."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The products from the Replenishment Rules you triggered are here but not all "
"products have\n"
"        Replenishment Rules at this stage. For some products or other "
"suppliers you need, you can\n"
"        chose to add them manually to a Purchase Order and even create new "
"Purchase Orders."
msgstr ""
"Produk-produk dari Aturan Replenishment yang Anda picu ada di sini, tetapi "
"tidak semua produk memiliki\n"
"        Aturan Replenishment pada tahap ini. Untuk beberapa produk atau "
"pemasok lain yang Anda butuhkan, Anda dapat\n"
"        memilih untuk menambahkannya secara manual ke Purchase Order dan "
"bahkan membuat Purchase Order baru."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Then go to the Operations &gt; Scrap menu and create a new entry."
msgstr "Kemudian, buka menu Operasi &gt; Pembuangan dan buat entri baru."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There is some stock of Buckets and Dispensers so no need to order some for "
"the ongoing\n"
"        period.<br/>However, you need to order Mayonnaise Buckets to meet "
"your forecast!"
msgstr ""
"Tersedia stok Ember dan Dispenser, jadi tidak perlu memesan untuk periode\n"
"        saat ini.<br/>Namun, Anda perlu memesan Ember Mayones untuk memenuhi "
"perkiraan!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There now is a smart button at the top of the Purchase Order to reach the "
"associated\n"
"        delivery. Hit the Deliveries smart button to open the delivery."
msgstr ""
"Kini terdapat tombol cerdas di bagian atas Purchase Order untuk mengakses\n"
"        pengiriman terkait. Klik tombol cerdas Pengiriman untuk membuka "
"detail pengiriman."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"Semua ini bisa Anda akses gratis dengan langgananmu saat ini. Jangan ragu "
"untuk menjelajahinya! 🙃"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This is great but you might be producing more Mayonnaise than you planned to "
"package..."
msgstr ""
"Sudah bagus, tapi mungkin Anda akan memproduksi lebih banyak mayones "
"daripada yang direncanakan untuk dikemas..."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup relies on Odoo's standard MTO capability: Potato Fresh Salad "
"operation routes include the MTO route."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan ini mengandalkan fitur MTO standar Odoo: rute operasi Potato "
"Fresh Salad mencakup rute MTO."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To bundle MO expected on close dates, select them from the list and fire the "
"Merge command from the Actions menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggabungkan MO yang diperkirakan akan ditutup pada tanggal tertentu, "
"pilih MO tersebut dari daftar dan jalankan perintah Gabung dari menu "
"Tindakan."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To save time and prevent mistake of typo in the Lot inputs, you might want "
"to work with <strong>Barcode\n"
"          App</strong>!"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghemat waktu dan mencegah kesalahan ketik pada input Lot, coba "
"<strong>Aplikasi\n"
"          Barcode</strong>!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.res_config_settings_form_view_inherited
msgid "Traceability"
msgstr "Bisa Ditelusuri"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_15
msgid "Tub 250g"
msgstr "Tub 250g"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:food_distribution.field_x_nutritional_facts_unit
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:food_distribution.field_x_product_template_nutritional_fact_unit
msgid "Unit"
msgstr "Unit"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Maintenance App</font>\n"
"        </strong> to keep all your work\n"
"        centers up and running."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Aplikasi Maintenance</font>\n"
"        </strong> untuk memastikan semua pusat kerja Anda\n"
"        tetap beroperasi dengan lancar."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Validate the delivery to your customer to complete the job."
msgstr "Validasi pengiriman ke pelanggan untuk menyelesaikan pekerjaan."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Validate the scrap order ensuring total isolation of the contaminated batch "
"from your supply chain."
msgstr ""
"Validasi order pembuangan (scrap) untuk memastikan isolasi total dari batch "
"yang terkontaminasi dari supply chain Anda."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_4
msgid "Vinegar"
msgstr "Cuka"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"We take the example of the mayonnaise here.<br/>Instead of producing buckets "
"when your customers ask for it, you anticipate the trends over the coming "
"weeks and months to always have some available and smoothen the production "
"workload."
msgstr ""
"Kita ambil contoh mayones di sini.<br/>Alih-alih memproduksi dalam jumlah "
"besar saat pelanggan memintanya, Anda mengantisipasi tren dalam beberapa "
"minggu dan bulan mendatang agar selalu memiliki stok yang tersedia dan "
"meringankan beban kerja produksi."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When hovering the on the Order button for a product Replenishment, a cell is "
"highlighted.\n"
"        Clicking this button orders the corresponding product for that "
"period according to the\n"
"        Replenishment input.<br/>This creates a manufacturing order or a "
"purchase order depending\n"
"        on the product configuration."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengarahkan kursor ke tombol Pesan untuk Replenishment produk, sebuah "
"sel akan disorot.\n"
"        Jika tombol ini diklik, produk yang bersangkutan untuk periode "
"tersebut akan terpesan sesuai dengan\n"
"        input Replenishment.<br/>Hal ini akan membuat manufacturing order "
"atau purchase order tergantung\n"
"        konfigurasi produknya."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When the truck arrives and you add those to your stock, validate the "
"delivery to update\n"
"        your stock levels. Don't forget to set the Lot reference in the "
"details of the delivery\n"
"        lines. You're now ready to product Mayonnaise for some time!"
msgstr ""
"Saat truk tiba dan Anda menambahkan produk tersebut ke stok, validasi "
"pengiriman untuk memperbarui\n"
"        tingkat stok Anda. Jangan lupa untuk menetapkan referensi Lot di "
"detail baris pengiriman\n"
"        tersebut. Anda kini siap memproduksi Mayones untuk beberapa waktu ke "
"depan!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While you are using <strong>Inventory App</strong>, open the product catalog "
"from the\n"
"        Products menu. This gives you a more comprehensive view of the "
"different products you\n"
"        manipulate."
msgstr ""
"Saat Anda menggunakan <strong>Aplikasi Inventaris</strong>, buka katalog "
"produk dari\n"
"        menu Produk. Anda akan mendapatkan gambaran yang lebih komprehensif "
"mengenai berbagai produk yang Anda\n"
"        kelola."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Working on your pricing to optimize your margin? You leverage the \"Compute "
"Price from\n"
"          BoM\" action available from the Product form or any Products list."
msgstr ""
"Menyusun harga untuk mengoptimalkan margin? Anda dapat memanfaatkan tindakan "
"\"Hitung Harga dari\n"
"          BoM\" yang tersedia di formulir Produk atau daftar Produk mana pun."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Apakah Anda ingin mendiskusikan lebih lanjut setup Odoo Anda dengan kami "
"atau melanjutkan tur?"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are ready to sign your first customers? To do so, open the Sales App, "
"create a new\n"
"        order and the customer."
msgstr ""
"Siap mendapatkan pelanggan pertama? Untuk melakukannya, buka Aplikasi Sales, "
"buat\n"
"        pesanan baru dan pelanggan."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Semua Aplikasi yang terpasang di database Odoo Anda bisa diakses melalui "
"dasbor utama."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily maintain from here for each product its list of ingredients, "
"the nutritional facts and specific notes to add to the label."
msgstr ""
"Dari sini, Anda dapat mengelola daftar bahan, fakta gizi, dan catatan khusus "
"untuk setiap produk yang akan ditambahkan ke label."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now hurry to manufacture the needed products, deliver them prior "
"sending the invoice\n"
"      to bill your customer."
msgstr ""
"Anda kini dapat segera memanufaktur produk yang dibutuhkan, mengirimkannya "
"sebelum mengirimkan faktur\n"
"      untuk menagih pelanggan Anda."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that the replenishment for the Mayonnaise comes as multiple of "
"the batch\n"
"          size. You can adjust this editing the Mayonnaise Production "
"Schedule from the pen icon\n"
"          near its name."
msgstr ""
"Terlihat bahwa replenishment untuk Mayones dilakukan dalam beberapa ukuran\n"
"          batch. Anda dapat menyesuaikannya dengan mengedit Jadwal Produksi "
"Mayones melalui ikon pena\n"
"          di dekat namanya."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see the forecast clicking the chart icon. Down below, you can see "
"that this is\n"
"          the\n"
"          outcome of all the planned Manufacturing Orders..."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat melihat perkiraan dengan mengeklik ikon grafik. Di bawah ini, "
"terlihat bahwa ini adalah\n"
"          hasil\n"
"          dari semua Manufacturing Order yang direncanakan..."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see you're about to get low on Vinegar and Mustard in the Forecast."
msgstr ""
"Terlihat bahwa persediaan Cuka dan Mustard Anda akan segera habis di "
"Prakiraan."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can setup your Bill of Material to reflect on you production processes "
"with or\n"
"          without steps, with embedded quality checks like in this example "
"or after a production."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengatur Bill of Material agar sesuai dengan proses produksi "
"dengan atau\n"
"          tanpa langkah-langkah, dengan menyelipkan pemeriksaan kualitas "
"seperti pada contoh ini atau setelah proses produksi."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo\n"
"          setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Anda telah berhasil menyelesaikan contoh demo kasus penggunaan ini! Ada "
"banyak cara untuk menyesuaikan pengaturan Odoo\n"
"          agar sesuai dengan kebutuhan bisnis Anda."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade\n"
"          your Food Distribution package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"Belum mengimpor data demo? Anda masih bisa melakukannya. Buka Aplikasi &gt; "
"Industri &gt; Upgrade\n"
"          paket Distribusi Makanan Anda dan centang kotak terkait"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for <strong>Food distribution</strong> package. "
"By doing so, we\n"
"      have installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your business "
"efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Anda baru saja menginstal paket Odoo untuk <strong>Distribusi Makanan</"
"strong>. Dengan demikian, kami\n"
"      telah menginstal sejumlah aplikasi yang diperlukan untuk menjalankan "
"bisnis Anda secara efisien."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might distribute different types of products, shelf-stable and "
"perishable, and therefore we have different ways to help you with "
"<strong>Manufacturing App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Anda mungkin mendistribusikan berbagai jenis produk, baik yang tahan lama "
"maupun yang mudah busuk, dan oleh karena itu kami memiliki berbagai cara "
"untuk membantu Anda melalui <strong>Aplikasi Manufaktur</strong>."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might have tested this package with or without demo data. In any case, "
"you may have\n"
"      written records in journals which are not deletable and which might be "
"an issue for your\n"
"      traceability."
msgstr ""
"Anda mungkin telah menguji paket ini dengan atau tanpa data demo.\n"
"      Yang mana pun itu, Anda mungkin telah menulis record di jurnal yang "
"tidak dapat dihapus\n"
"      dan hal ini mungkin menjadi masalah bagi pelacakan Anda."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You registered your first lot of Mayonnaise. Note that it is possible to "
"change the lot\n"
"          number prefix from the product form, in the Inventory tab."
msgstr ""
"Anda telah mendaftarkan lot Mayones pertama. Perhatikan bahwa hanya\n"
"          awalan nomor lot yang dapat diubah dari formulir produk, di tab "
"Inventaris."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you\n"
"      can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menjalankan alur-alur berikut untuk melihat gambaran tentang "
"berbagai\n"
"      proses yang dapat dengan cepat dijalankan menggunakan paket ini di "
"Odoo."

